<script type="text/template" id="transcriber-bugs-widget-template">
  <div class="left">
    <div class="input_field">
      <input type="text" placeholder="" />
      <a href="#" class="btn ok">ok</a>
      <a href="#" class="btn error">!</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="right">
    <a href="#" class="back">Back</a>
    <a href="#" class="skip">Skip</a>
    <a href="#" class="step"></a>
    <a href="#" class="btn finish">Next Record</a>
  </div>
</script>

<script type="text/template" id="popup-template">
  <div class="content">
    <p>Welcome to CalBugs on Notes from Nature and thank you for helping us transcribe specimen records.</p>
    <p>Insects and spiders may seem a little alien to us, but they make up a huge and important part of the biodiversity of our planet. Our natural history collections are full of millions of specimens of bugs, which have been collected over the last 100 years or more. These specimens can tell us a lot of important things about the health and future of the environment.</p>
    <p>However, data from insect collections are notoriously difficult to digitize since most insect are pinned with small data labels directly underneath the specimens. The imagining gurus at CalBugs have perfected methods of removing the labels and getting great photos. Now we need your help getting the information from labels into a form where the textual content can be more effectively databased and used for documenting biodiversity and studying its changes.</p>
    <p>To start the process we have transcribed the species name for each record, so we have that information in hand. What we donâ€™t have, is all the other information, such as the locality where the specimen was found, the date it was collected, etc. You can provide that via a step-by-step process of adding in what you see on the labels into the right spots using your transcribing tool!</p>
    <button>Got it. Let me transcribe!</button>
  </div>
</script>

<script type="text/template" id="closer-template">
  <a href="#" class="close"></a>
</script>

<script type="text/template" id="highlight-template">
  <a href="#" class="close"></a>
</script>

<script type="text/template" id="helper-template">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="sub-container">
      <div class="toggle">Show Help Text</div>
      <div class="title"></div>
      <div class="description"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</script>

<script type="text/template" id="launcher-template">
  <span>Drag a square around the specimen label</span> 
  <a href="#" class="example" data-src="images/sernac.png">See example</a>
  <a href="#" class="btn start hidden">Start this record</a>
  <a href="#" class="skip">Skip this record</a>
</script>

<script type="text/template" id="date-input-template">
  <div class="date_field month"><input type="text" name="month" class="month" placeholder="month" /></div> 
  <div class="date_field day"><input type="text" name="day" class="day" placeholder="day" /></div> 
  <div class="date_field year"><input type="text" name="year" class="year" placeholder="year" /></div>
</script>

<script type="text/template" id="latlng-input-template">
  <div class="latlng_field lat"><input type="text" name="lat" class="lat" placeholder="latitude"></div> 
  <div class="latlng_field lng"><input type="text" name="lng" class="lng" placeholder="longitude"></div> 
</script>

<script type="text/template" id="tooltip-error-template">
  <strong class="title">{{title}}</strong>
  <div class="description">{{description}}</div>
  <div class="tip"></div>
</script>

<script type="text/template" id="tooltip-step-template">
  <ul>
    {{#links}}
    <li><a href="#">{{title}}</a><span></span></li>
    {{/links}}
  </ul>
  <div class="tip"></div>
</script>

<script type="text/template" id="tooltip-template">
  <strong class="title">{{{ title }}}</strong>
  <div class="description">{{{ description }}}</div>

  <div class="buttons">
    <a href="#" class="btn main">{{ main }}</a> 
    <a href="#" class="btn secondary">{{ secondary }}</a>
  </div>

  <div class="tip"></div>
</script>

<script type="text/template" id="tooltip-example-template">
  <div class="buttons"><a href="#/archives/Herbarium" class="btn main">{{ main }}</a></div> 
  <div class="tip"></div>
</script>

<script type="text/template" id="statusbar-template">
  <div class="left">
    <h1 class="title">{{ title }}</h1>
    <h3 class="description">{{ description }}</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="right">

    <div class="separator"></div>

    <div class="count">
      <div class="counter">0</div>
      <strong>Records done</strong>
    </div>

    <div class="separator"></div>

    <div class="off">
      <a href="/" class="btn close"></a>
    </div>

  </div>
</script>
